title: New York U.S. House 26th District Results: Brian Higgins Wins

maintext:
Representative Brian Higgins won the United States House of Representatives 26th District race in New York on Tuesday. Higgins is up by 49 points with all precincts reporting.
Below are detailed results for the race. View other New York election results on our full New York results page. See all races on our House map.
